channel.title: Help! No response from server, please try using a different world error
channel.description: So anyways, i used to have a few rsps, and i decided, well Ill make a new one. So I downloaded a few sources and clients, made sure the ip in the client was 127.0.0.1 so i could log in, and every client or source i download i get an error saying "No response from server please try using a different world." Can anyone help me?
